{"tid":1508423,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"魚蛋個陣都講過向天開槍違例，而家再衰多次","createTime":"2019-08-26T13:52:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T15:37:31.000Z","uid":284343,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"93d80bbcc7d785df971b2f18e406cb9fa2c08b06","tid":1508423,"uid":284343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:52:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QfRBRMo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQfRBRMo.jpg&h=843fff3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n［黑警向天開槍屬違反警例 Madam Yu：表現英勇克制？？？］<br />\n昨晚於荃灣發生了警察向天鳴槍，試圖驅散人群，更向跪在地上、求警察不要再對人群及示威者開槍之市民，直接以腳踢開市民，以及揮舞警槍，叫該市民走開，可見現在的香港警察的濫暴已成日常。<br />\n但有市民眼尖發現，原來當時警察開槍不是為了驅散示威者，而是要掩護無能同僚之跌槍事故；請參考Source 2當時聽到一下槍聲以後，隨後即看到有警員徬徨撿槍，可見當時為警察一時情急，因此突然向天鳴槍而恐嚇民眾，好讓同僚有時間撿回掉在地上的配槍。<br />\n不過據了解及翻查過程資料後發現，向天開槍該行為屬違規；早於2016年的魚蛋革命當時，亦有同類型事件發生，當時 Stand News 立場新聞 就警員向天連開2槍一事，與擁有多年輔警經驗之前輔警進行訪問，表示根據警隊內部有關槍械訓練的手槍安全防禦法指引，向天開槍之舉動已違反第四點：「切勿將槍械指向任何不欲射擊之人物或物件。」，以及第六點：「如未能確定目標，切勿開槍」<br />\n但如今相隔3年後，警察公共關係科高級警司余鎧均竟聲稱，向天開槍此行為為「表現英勇、克制」，另外對腳踢市民之事件，更辯稱為「自然反應」，可見警察如今對警隊內的各種惡行，已選擇視若無睹、縱容警隊濫暴之風，實屬無恥、可恥之舉！<br />\n<br />\n能清楚聽到開槍的聲音（00:35)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/RTHKVNEWS/videos/1356270081202621/?t=34\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FRTHKVNEWS%2Fvideos%2F1356270081202621%2F%3Ft%3D34&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsTKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=ff2f5371\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/RTHKVNEWS/videos/1356270081202621/?t=34</a><br />\n<br />\n跌槍事件參考：<br />\nSource 1: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1505733/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1505733/page/1</a><br />\nSource 2(請從2:06開始看起）：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/socrec/videos/657655694735292/?t=126\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsocrec%2Fvideos%2F657655694735292%2F%3Ft%3D126&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsTKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=1f8e5c29\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/socrec/videos/657655694735292/?t=126</a><br />\n<br />\n向天開槍違規：<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/旺角騷亂-前輔警-根據警例-不得向天開槍/?fbclid=IwAR26fpzi0zkHirW8phxyCGaORl-xND9brUBFyS3AMk0N9yYRtkcK2T5mxHg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92%E9%A8%B7%E4%BA%82-%E5%89%8D%E8%BC%94%E8%AD%A6-%E6%A0%B9%E6%93%9A%E8%AD%A6%E4%BE%8B-%E4%B8%8D%E5%BE%97%E5%90%91%E5%A4%A9%E9%96%8B%E6%A7%8D%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR26fpzi0zkHirW8phxyCGaORl-xND9brUBFyS3AMk0N9yYRtkcK2T5mxHg&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsTKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=9da443da\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92%E9%A8%B7%E4%BA%82-%E5%89%8D%E8%BC%94%E8%AD%A6-%E6%A0%B9%E6%93%9A%E8%AD%A6%E4%BE%8B-%E4%B8%8D%E5%BE%97%E5%90%91%E5%A4%A9%E9%96%8B%E6%A7%8D%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR26fpzi0zkHirW8phxyCGaORl-xND9brUBFyS3AMk0N9yYRtkcK2T5mxHg&h=66d9d549\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/旺角騷亂-前輔警-根據警例-不得向天開槍/?fbclid=IwAR26fpzi0zkHirW8phxyCGaORl-xND9brUBFyS3AMk0N9yYRtkcK2T5mxHg</a><br />\n<br />\nRef：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/MadameMlovesmurmur/photos/a.171117426743292/651572692031094/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FMadameMlovesmurmur%2Fphotos%2Fa.171117426743292%2F651572692031094%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsTKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=c1c52ab8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/MadameMlovesmurmur/photos/a.171117426743292/651572692031094/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"9146336ddae189bec040a8e10cd38c1dfbe3482c","tid":1508423,"uid":52230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:54:03.000Z","msg":"牙蛇開槍唔洗你教<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af5925f1b7a79f01553ec097e1a98efc3947e2e4","tid":1508423,"uid":70332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:57